            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Yeah it seems that the parsed TS tree is out of sync with the buffer. The buffer is probably changed _while iterating_ the query matches. Easiest option is to put the `parser:parse()` call closer to the `iter_matches` code. Maybe that helps. Otherwise we can (1) ignore the errors with `pcall`'s or (2) retry on errors.",
